precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a SUPPLEMENTARY
AGREEMENT to the AGREEMENT ON SOCIAL SECURITY between Canada and the
PHILIPPINES, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing other
representatives to sign the Agreement on behalf of Canada.
